  "remarks": "OJSC Special Design Bureau of Instrument Engineering and Automation (OJSC “SKB PA”) is a company active in Russia’s military and industrial complex, specialised in the development and creation of electrohydraulic, electromechanical, navigation and control systems for mobile civil and special-purpose equipment. OJSC “SKB PA” holds licences for handling state secrets and developing military equipment.",
